{"id":1173312,"date":[{"year":1998,"month":10,"day":23}],"page":"4","source":"本报","region":"","masthead":"画刊","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"393","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我们共同的节日","ftitle":"——’98上海旅游节剪影","authors":["许政泓"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>吉祥物“乐乐”笑迎四方客。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>张锁庆</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>万众欢聚大世界，再现申城昔日景。张锁庆摄</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>你追我赶，一场摇快船的比赛开始了。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040204.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“我来教你”，美国游客面对螺蛳，不知从何下口!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040205.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>真如古镇装扮一新，民俗风情多姿多彩。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040206.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>湖心亭畔、九曲桥边都留下了远方客人的身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040207.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>金秋十月，上海街头五彩缤纷，热闹非凡。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040208.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>左:张灯结彩的街头，喜庆’98上海旅游节。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040209.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>右:轻歌曼舞使节庆的气氛更浓。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040210.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>来自全国各地的游客，在人民广场观赏白鸽。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040211.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>静安区举办的“金秋欢乐之夜”上，市民们跳起了欢乐舞。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040212.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>又一台精彩文艺节目开始演出了。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040213.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>美国游客来到居民家中“学做一天上海人”。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040214.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>上海人的结婚盛典引起外国游客浓厚兴趣。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040215.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>青浦县的水乡旅游盛会吸引了成千上万的中外游客。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\10\\98an040216.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>徐裕根,杭凌冰,傅国林</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>松江“上海之根游”拉开了帷幕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本版摄影除署名外均为本报记者傅国林、杭凌冰、徐裕根摄　版面设计:许政泓</FONT>"}]}